      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must cover the operating envelope defined in the COU, including the range of flow rates and rotational speeds for the CPB application.",
      "rationale": "Validation dataset spans 3 to 7 L/min flow rate and 2000 to 3500 RPM, fully encompassing the 5 COU operating points. Pump geometry matches the FDA generic centrifugal pump used as predicate reference. Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU operating envelope."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
