      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence must be demonstrated with residuals below 1e-5 for all transport equations and monitored quantities of interest stabilized.",
      "rationale": "All simulations converged to residuals below 1e-6 for continuity, momentum, and turbulence equations. NIH monitor values stabilized to less than 0.1% change over the final 500 iterations. Solver error contribution assessed as negligible relative to discretization error."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
