      "acceptanceCriteria": "Key model inputs (fluid viscosity, pump geometry, boundary conditions) must be traceable to measurement data with documented uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "All model inputs traceable to measurement sources: pump geometry from manufacturer CAD (tolerance ±0.02 mm), fluid properties from rheometry measurements (viscosity uncertainty ±2%), boundary conditions from flow bench measurements (flow rate uncertainty ±1.5%). Input uncertainty propagation performed via Latin hypercube sampling (n=50)."
