    "rationale": "The CFD model for CPB hemolysis prediction has been assessed at High assurance level. All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate NIH prediction accuracy within the 15% acceptance threshold across all COU operating points. Geometric sensitivity validation confirms reliable trend prediction for dimensional tolerance assessment. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and supporting the RH < 1 submission criterion for the Class II CPB device.",
